name: Add docstrings to all public functions and classes
scope: python
language: python
severity: warning
if: Public functions or classes without docstrings
then: Add comprehensive docstrings with parameters, return values, and examples
why: Docstrings provide essential documentation for code usage and maintenance.
globs: ["src/**/*.py"]

---
name: Document field classifications in model comments
scope: python
language: python
severity: error
if: Model fields without classification comments
then: Add comments like # (MANUAL) description or # (CALCULATED) description
why: Field classification prevents manual setting of calculated fields and documents intent.
globs: ["src/**/models.py"]

---
name: Update README.md for significant changes
scope: markdown
language: markdown
severity: warning
if: Making significant changes without updating README.md
then: Update README.md to reflect new features, setup instructions, or architecture changes
why: README.md is the first point of contact for new developers and users.
globs: ["README.md", "docs/**/*.md"]

---
name: Document API endpoints with examples
scope: python
language: python
severity: warning
if: API endpoints without docstrings or examples
then: Add comprehensive docstrings with request/response examples
why: API documentation helps frontend developers and external consumers.
globs: ["src/api.py", "src/api/**/*.py"]

---
name: Comment complex business logic
scope: python
language: python
severity: warning
if: Complex calculations or business rules without comments
then: Add comments explaining the business logic and calculation steps
why: Business logic comments help future developers understand financial calculations.
globs: ["src/**/*.py"]

---
name: Document domain method parameters
scope: python
language: python
severity: warning
if: Domain methods without parameter documentation
then: Document all parameters, especially session parameter requirements
why: Clear parameter documentation prevents usage errors and improves maintainability.
globs: ["src/**/*.py"]

---
name: Add type hints to function signatures
scope: python
language: python
severity: warning
if: Functions without type hints
then: Add type hints to improve code readability and IDE support
why: Type hints provide documentation and catch type-related errors.
globs: ["src/**/*.py"]

---
name: Document domain method parameters comprehensively
scope: python
language: python
severity: warning
if: Domain methods without comprehensive docstrings including parameters, return values, and usage examples
then: Add docstrings with @param, @return, and @example sections
why: Clear documentation prevents usage errors and improves maintainability.
globs: ["src/**/*.py"]
